metadata.name: Colt Torres
metadata.description:
"Precision beats power..."

The name Torres is synonymous with greatness in South America. They are the pride of professional wrasslin in Ecuador. The youngest lion of the pride comes to show what someone quick as a cat can bring to MWF.

His speed could be the great equalizer when you try to take on this third generation star. Colt wants to hit first, hit often, and count on the fact you can't kill what you can't catch.
